quran[8{c,v,t}:
40,59,"yaqeenan qayamat ki gharri anay wali hai, is ke anay mein koi shak nahi, magar aksar log nahi mantay"
40,60,"tumhara rab kehta hai"" mujhe poukaro, mein tumhari duayen qubool karoon ga, jo log ghamand mein aa kar meri ibadat se mun morty hain, zaroor woh zaleel o khawar ho kar jahannum mein daakhil hon ge """
40,61,"woh Allah hi to hai jis ne tumahray liye raat banai taakay is mein sukoon haasil karo, aur din ko roshan kya haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah logon par bara fazl frmane wala hai magar aksar log shukar ada nahi karte"
40,62,wohi Allah ( jis ne tumahray liye yeh kuch kya hai ) tumhara rab hai har cheez ka khaaliq is ke siwa koi mabood nahi phir tum kidhar se b_hkaye ja rahay ho ?
40,63,isi terhan woh sab log b_hkaye jatay rahay hain jo Allah ki ayaat ka inkaar karte thay
40,64,woh Allah hi to hai jis ne tumahray liye zameen ko jaye qarar banaya aur oopar aasman ka gunbad bana diya jis ne tumhari soorat banai aur barri hi umdah banai jis ne tumhe pakeeza cheezon ka rizaq diya wohi Allah ( jis ke yeh kaam hain ) tumhara rab hai be hisaab barkatoon wala hai woh kaayenaat ka rab
40,65,wohi zindah hai uss ke siwa koi mabood nahi usi ko tum poukaro apne deen ko is ke liye khalis kar ke saari tareef Allah Rab alaalmin hi ke liye hai
40,66,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn logon se keh do ke mujhe to unn hstyon ki ibadat se mana kar diya gaya hai jinhein tum Allah ko chore kar pkarte ho ( mein yeh kaam kaisay kar sakta hon ) jabkay mere paas mere rab ki taraf se بینات aa chuki hain mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke mein rab alaalmin ke agay sar-e tasleem khham kar dun"
